data.name: Unregister.Name
data.value: Command name to be unregistered. Can use wildcards like '*'

data.name: ArgumentCompleter
data.value: ScriptBlock that returns completion candidates for command arguments.

data.name: NoFileCompletions
data.value: No file or directory completion in command argument completion.

data.name: CommandParameterStyle
data.value: Style of the command parameters. Defaults to "GNU", Long option prefix to '--', Short option prefix to '-', and Value sparator to '='. "Windows" will have the option prefix to '/' and Value separator to ':'.

data.name: DelegateArgumentIndex
data.value: Argument index of a command to delegate completions. e.g.) `sudo {COMMAND} [args...]`, `time {COMMAND} [args...]` Specifies the index of the argument that will be "{COMMAND}". (starting from 0)

data.name: Force
data.value: Forcibly overwrite even if already registered.

data.name: Error.AlreadyRegistered
data.value: Failed to register completer: "{0}". Maybe it's already registered.
